# orcasecurity_admission_controller_policy_assignment (Resource)

Provides an Admission Controller policy assignment (the API calls it a "scope"): attaches policies to Kubernetes clusters, cloud accounts, or the whole organization.

At least one of `full_organization = true`, `clusters`, or `cloud_accounts` must be set.

